00:16:10.303 --> 00:16:12.389 position:50% align:center
"Oh, in the usual room, right?"

00:16:12.472 --> 00:16:13.723 position:50% align:center
[FROG DOCTOR]
Yep.

00:16:13.807 --> 00:16:15.141 position:50% align:center
Then Misaka Misaka
will run off in that direction,

00:16:15.225 --> 00:16:18.144 position:50% align:center
