only her words behind!

00:16:18.228 --> 00:16:19.729 position:50% align:center
Whoosh! Bye!

00:16:20.939 --> 00:16:23.149 position:50% align:center
And by the way, at the
request of Anti-Skill,

00:16:23.233 --> 00:16:25.276 position:50% align:center
I conducted a thorough
examination of that girl

00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:27.737 position:50% align:center
