by that point.

00:16:36.538 --> 00:16:38.331 position:50% align:center
[ACCELERATOR]
Not interested.

00:16:38.415 --> 00:16:39.457 position:50% align:center
[FROG DOCTOR]
One thing.

00:16:39.541 --> 00:16:40.625 position:50% align:center
I found this.

00:16:40.709 --> 00:16:42.627 position:50% align:center
Oddly enough,
it was in her mouth.

00:16:46.506 --> 00:16:49.592 position:50% align:center
