00:16:51.344 --> 00:16:52.846 position:50% align:center
What is it?

00:16:52.929 --> 00:16:54.723 position:50% align:center
[ESTHER]
A low-level spiritual charm.

00:16:54.806 --> 00:16:55.890 position:50% align:center
A charm?

00:16:55.974 --> 00:16:58.018 position:50% align:center
I'm going to need
your help once again.

00:17:04.524 --> 00:17:06.651 position:50% align:center
[ESTHER] My family invented
a type of necromancy

00:17:06.735 --> 00:17:09.112 position:50% align:center
that allows us to
transplant a false soul.

00:17:09.195 --> 00:17:12.323 position:50% align:center
Once it's been attached to
a corpse, we can control it.

00:17:12.407 --> 00:17:15.535 position:50% align:center
This poor girl.
She's more than a dead body.

00:17:16.619 --> 00:17:18.580 position:50% align:center
She's a person.

00:17:18.663 --> 00:17:20.582 position:50% align:center
I shared the secrets
of necromancy

00:17:20.665 --> 00:17:24.336 position:50% align:center
without fully understanding
the consequences.

00:17:24.419 --> 00:17:27.589 position:50% align:center
Even after I was warned to be
careful who I taught them to.

00:17:29.257 --> 00:17:30.967 position:50% align:center
And here's the result.

00:17:31.051 --> 00:17:33.636 position:50% align:center
A life lost for an
abominable cause.

00:17:38.183 --> 00:17:40.894 position:50% align:center
All right.
Let's have a look inside.

00:17:44.439 --> 00:17:47.567 position:50% align:center
