just like I thought.

00:17:47.650 --> 00:17:51.112 position:50% align:center
If left this way, it'll invite
in residual information.

00:17:51.196 --> 00:17:53.656 position:50% align:center
We couldn't bury
Hasami Hitokawa in a grave.

00:17:53.740 --> 00:17:55.658 position:50% align:center
She'd just crawl out of it.

00:17:55.742 --> 00:17:57.077 position:50% align:center
And not only that...

00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:59.371 position:50% align:center
If her vessel remains
trapped in this current state,

00:17:59.454 --> 00:18:02.248 position:50% align:center
she'll never be able to pass
through the gates of Heaven.

00:18:02.332 --> 00:18:03.958 position:50% align:center
Hasami Hitokawa.

00:18:04.042 --> 00:18:05.627 position:50% align:center
I'll reanimate you

00:18:05.710 --> 00:18:08.505 position:50% align:center
by using my Huotou,
a false soul I created.

00:18:08.588 --> 00:18:11.466 position:50% align:center
I'll take possession of you
and close the spiritual conduit.

00:18:13.218 --> 00:18:15.220 position:50% align:center
[ACCELERATOR]
Is this her ability?

00:18:15.303 --> 00:18:17.013 position:50% align:center
She must be using
history and legend

00:18:17.097 --> 00:18:19.724 position:50% align:center
to reinforce her own paradigm,

00:18:19.808 --> 00:18:22.227 position:50% align:center
and then extending out
her Personal Reality.

00:18:23.228 --> 00:18:24.854 position:50% align:center
You'll be all right now.

00:18:27.315 --> 00:18:28.983 position:50% align:center
[ACCELERATOR gasps]

00:18:29.067 --> 00:18:30.235 position:50% align:center
[ACCELERATOR]
What is that?

00:18:32.070 --> 00:18:32.862 position:50% align:center
[ACCELERATOR]
Her brain?

00:18:32.946 --> 00:18:34.114 position:50% align:center
Don't touch it!

00:18:34.739 --> 00:18:36.074 position:50% align:center
[ACCELERATOR gasps]

00:18:37.826 --> 00:18:38.868 position:50% align:center
Hasami?

00:18:40.662 --> 00:18:41.913 position:50% align:center
Almost!

00:18:43.581 --> 00:18:45.750 position:50% align:center
