00:19:51.399 --> 00:19:52.901 position:50% align:center
[HITOKAWA]
What?

00:19:52.984 --> 00:19:53.943 position:50% align:center
[ALPHA TEAM 02B]
Understood.

00:19:54.027 --> 00:19:55.862 position:50% align:center
Commencing with disposal.

